==English==
{{wp|Aristocracy}}

===Etymology===
{{root|en|ine-pro|*h₂er-}}
From {{bor|en|fr|aristocrate||aristocrat}}, attested once in the 16th century but recoined in the {{w|French Revolution|Revolutionary}} era, from {{m|fr|aristocratie||aristocracy}}, from {{der|en|la-med|aristocratia}}, from {{der|en|grc|ἀριστοκρατία}}, from {{m|grc|ἄριστος||best}} (compare {{cog|ang|ar}}) + {{m|grc|κράτος||rule}}. {{surf|en|aristo-|-crat}}.

===Pronunciation===
